snippet.title: The Henry Stickmin Collection Announcement
snippet.description:
The Henry Stickmin Collection is set to release in 2020! Play all the previous games in remastered glory! As well as... A finale?

Add it to your Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1089980/The_Henry_Stickmin_Collection/
